you know.

02:31.496 --> 02:34.040
Farzanna was like a cat
that got the cream.

02:35.580 --> 02:37.080
(WHISTLING STOPS)

02:37.748 --> 02:39.580
I am pleased for her though.

02:40.288 --> 02:42.124
I think she's gonna make
a good gran.

02:43.708 --> 02:45.708
(SONG CONTINUES PLAYING)

02:49.748 --> 02:51.580
(MARY HUMMING ALONG)

02:57.164 --> 02:58.580
It'll need to brew.

03:04.624 --> 03:05.832
Love?

03:05.916 --> 03:07.080
Ahmed, love?

