(BIRDS SQUAWKING)

18:41.248 --> 18:43.080
(DOG BARKING IN DISTANCE)

19:03.120 --> 19:04.620
(WHIRRING)

19:12.496 --> 19:13.664
(WHIRRING STOPS)

19:17.204 --> 19:18.288
Hello.

19:20.040 --> 19:21.540
My name is Mary.

19:25.164 --> 19:26.164
Hello.

19:26.248 --> 19:27.748
I'm Ahmed's wife.

19:31.956 --> 19:33.040
Hello.

19:44.912 --> 19:46.120
I'm Mary.

20:00.080 --> 20:01.288
(SNIFFLES)

20:16.664 --> 20:18.500
(DOORBELL RINGS)

20:22.208 --> 20:24.040
(FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING)

20:28.080 --> 20:29.208
(MARY GASPS)

20:30.080 --> 20:32.580
- Oh, er... Erm...

20:36.208 --> 20:37.788
- I...

20:41.708 --> 20:43.248
I'm sorry. I, erm...

20:43.832 --> 20:46.832
I'm confused.
You are here for the cleaning?

20:47.248 --> 20:49.080
(MOBILE RINGING)

20:49.956 --> 20:51.248
Just a sec.

20:58.580 --> 21:00.872
You can do it now
since you're here.

21:00.956 --> 21:02.372
But I never confirmed.

21:25.248 --> 21:27.080
(BLENDER WHIRRING)

21:34.208 --> 21:36.916
(WHIRRING STOPS)

21:54.288 --> 21:55.956
So you are English?

22:02.332 --> 22:04.164
When I saw you at the door,

22:05.540 --> 22:06.832
I wasn't sure.

22:07.456 --> 22:10.416
The last girl they sent left it,
you can use it if you like.

22:14.496 --> 22:15.788
I'm Geneviève.

22:20.248 --> 22:21.248
Mary.

22:24.540 --> 22:27.040
You don't speak any French?

22:27.580 --> 22:29.832
- (GRUNTS SOFTLY)
- Okay, I'm sure they told you...

22:29.916 --> 22:31.332
- (MOBILE RINGING)
- (SIGHS)

22:31.416 --> 22:33.580
I'm sure they told you, but, er,

22:33.664 --> 22:37.208
I just need someone for a very short
term to help me with the clear-up.

22:37.288 --> 22:39.248
You know,
before the movers come.

22:39.332 --> 22:42.248
So maybe, for today,
you can clean

22:42.332 --> 22:44.664
the bathroom and do laundry.

22:44.748 --> 22:46.248
(MOBILE CONTINUES RINGING)

22:47.748 --> 22:48.748
Okay?

22:49.208 --> 22:52.080
- Where are you moving to?
- Oh, we're staying in Calais.

22:53.248 --> 22:55.624
- When are you moving?
- Saturday.

22:55.708 --> 23:00.288
I know... I know I left this
far too late, but... (SIGHS)

23:00.372 --> 23:03.580
- (MOBILE RINGING)
- (SIGHS) Okay. Erm...

23:03.664 --> 23:06.580
Sorry, can I just leave you
down there to start here?

23:06.664 --> 23:09.580
And if you have any questions,
ask me.

23:10.496 --> 23:12.372
The cleaning detergent's there.

23:12.456 --> 23:14.332
Here. Okay?

23:16.748 --> 23:18.372
(SPEAKING FRENCH)

24:28.372 --> 24:29.664
Everything is okay?

24:29.748 --> 24:31.496
Mmm-hmm. Yeah.

24:53.832 --> 24:55.664
(WATER DRIPPING)

25:03.208 --> 25:05.624
(MOBILE RINGING IN DISTANCE)

25:07.372 --> 25:09.208
(GENEVIÈVE SPEAKING FRENCH)

25:10.708 --> 25:12.832
(DOOR OPENS AND CLOSES)

25:16.332 --> 25:18.164
(MUFFLED FOOTSTEPS)

25:40.080 --> 25:41.916
- (HIP-HOP MUSIC PLAYS ON
SPEAKERS) - GENEVIÈVE: Mary?

25:42.000 --> 25:43.624
I'm leaving.

25:45.416 --> 25:46.416
I've got to go now.

25:46.496 --> 25:50.164
So, I'll leave your wages on the
counter under the snow globe.

25:57.788 --> 25:59.832
(SONG CONTINUES PLAYING
ON SPEAKERS)

26:31.164 --> 26:32.248
(GRUNTS)

26:33.248 --> 26:35.416
(MELANCHOLY STRING MUSIC
PLAYING)

26:37.788 --> 26:39.288
(WAVES CRASHING)

26:56.040 --> 26:58.040
(MELANCHOLY STRING MUSIC
CONTINUES PLAYING)

27:45.248 --> 27:47.664
(BREATHING DEEPLY)

28:24.204 --> 28:26.040
(BREATHES SHAKILY)

28:39.372 --> 28:40.788
(DOORBELL RINGS)

28:43.000 --> 28:45.416
- (FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING)
- (DOOR OPENS)

28:57.040 --> 28:58.916
These are for charity donations,

28:59.000 --> 29:00.496
so they can go down.

29:02.748 --> 29:03.956
And...

29:06.580 --> 29:08.080
these can all go too.

29:10.164 --> 29:12.916
- What's wrong with these?
- Ahmed doesn't wear them.

29:14.956 --> 29:16.456
Solomon's father.

29:28.416 --> 29:31.080
Mary, don't worry
about folding them.

29:31.164 --> 29:32.456
They're just going in bags.

29:57.872 --> 29:58.956
(SIGHS)

30:22.788 --> 30:23.916
Okay?

30:30.000 --> 30:31.332
(GENEVIÈVE SPEAKS INDISTINCTLY)

30:33.664 --> 30:35.664
(MUTTERING IN ENGLISH) She doesn't
know what she's talking about.

30:36.580 --> 30:38.248
He wears these all the time.

30:38.704 --> 30:40.916
(GENEVIÈVE AND SOLOMON
CONVERSING IN FRENCH)

30:57.748 --> 30:59.288
MAN: (ON SPEAKERS) Solomon!

30:59.372 --> 31:01.788
Oh, yeah, come on!
Hello?

31:04.372 --> 31:05.788
MAN: Yeah, that's good!
(LAUGHING)

31:24.704 --> 31:26.748
(GENEVIÈVE SPEAKING FRENCH
ON TV)

31:34.124 --> 31:35.704
AHMED: (IN ENGLISH)
There we go again. There we go.

31:37.372 --> 31:38.912
Pick that one.

31:39.000 --> 31:41.080
- (GENEVIÈVE LAUGHS)
- (SOLOMON SPEAKING FRENCH)

31:43.248 --> 31:45.164
(GENEVIÈVE SPEAKING FRENCH)

31:47.748 --> 31:48.832
GENEVIÈVE: Oh.

32:01.496 --> 32:02.912
(SIGHS DEEPLY)

32:23.412 --> 32:24.872
(IN ENGLISH) Er, I'm finished.

32:27.372 --> 32:28.580
You have a light?

32:35.372 --> 32:36.496
Thank you.

32:59.000 --> 33:01.412
- Did you convert when you married? - Yes.

33:03.580 --> 33:05.788
How do you feel
about wearing it?

33:05.872 --> 33:07.124
- How do I feel?
- Mmm-hmm.

33:07.204 --> 33:08.540
I don't.

33:08.624 --> 33:10.124
I've worn it
longer than I haven't.

33:12.000 --> 33:14.412
It must have been hard
to take all that on?

33:17.124 --> 33:19.624
Back then I did something
for my husband

33:20.248 --> 33:22.124
that no one else could.

33:27.248 --> 33:28.748
- (KEYS JINGLING)
- Mary.

33:29.872 --> 33:31.124
The keys for you.

33:32.164 --> 33:33.288
(HANDS KEYS)

33:39.124 --> 33:40.332
See you tomorrow.

33:40.412 --> 33:42.248
(FOOTSTEPS RECEDING)

33:58.624 --> 34:00.124
(PRAYING IN ARABIC)

34:32.164 --> 34:34.164
(CONTINUES PRAYING TEARFULLY)

35:02.624 --> 35:04.124
(BREATHING SHAKILY)

35:06.456 --> 35:07.540
(SNIFFLES)

35:08.204 --> 35:10.040
(RESUMES PRAYING IN ARABIC)

35:13.704 --> 35:14.788
(SNIFFLES)

35:25.412 --> 35:27.248
